<table width=100%>
<tr>
<td width=50%><font color=white>Posted By: Toobubba</font></td><td width=50% align=right><font color=white>2000-06-01 17:25:17</font></td></tr><tr>
<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>Runed circlet is now the rare drop from preacher. Having camped this guy quite a bit lately, my experience has been that circlet drops about 1 in 3 times. Preacher doesn't spawn as much as he used to, either. On about a 25 minute cycle, spawn in preacher's spot may be a plain ol ice gob, an evoker, a wizard, a prelate, a priest, or the preacher himself. So figure you got a 1 in 6 chance of preacher spawning every 25 minutes. If your luck is only average, you'll be waiting an hour and fifteen minutes before you see a preacher, and you'll have to do that three times before you get your circlet. That's just the average, and your luck may be better or worse, but if you want this item, figure on 3 hrs and 45 minutes of boredom. Folks who have camped this thing before will prolly say I'm full of it, but before you do, give it a try. Things have changed with regard to this item.<BR>
<BR>
Toobubba Reddnek<BR>
36th level Ranger, Sol Ro<BR>
Knights of Evermore</font></td></tr></table>
