<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>I'm pretty sure the RC is the common drop and CIMS is the rare drop.  My fellow guild members (Sebas, Birch, and Nanuvil) and I, camped the preacher for about an hour and a half and looted three RCs and zero CIMS.  I'm not sure if we were lucky, but i'm glad we looted 3 RCs rather than 3 CIMS!<BR>
